{"tid":1486842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[ 眾籌突發 ] 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告","createTime":"2019-08-19T04:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T09:49:33.000Z","uid":271234,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a541ce46fb03d21f8befed21ca582e8603fc359c","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"<em>上一個post 唔記得貼眾籌 link , 再開 !</em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">眾籌 link:  <a href=\"https://shorturl.at/LRW57\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshorturl.at%2FLRW57&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=695db626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://shorturl.at/LRW57</a></span><br />\n<br />\n大家好, 本人謹代表團隊發出此次&quot;本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告&quot;眾籌！<br />\n始於一個月前藍絲已有影片廣告在youtube出現, 當時&quot;連登&quot;有不少人支持眾籌投放多媒體廣告，但都無下文；本人亦一直有為這個方向思考，直至近日運動越見嚴峻，而巧合身邊朋友亦能抽空幫忙，我們即時建立香港反送中運動記事錄網站，網站暫時以專題報導及遊行集會回顧兩大項目為主，將利用投放圖片廣告引起市民關注而進入網站特定主題，而每個主題亦針對5大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網站網址:  <a href=\"http://www.hkebill.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkebill.com&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=6c4a9890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkebill.com</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEEZzG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEEZzG4.jpg&h=479bcee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">針對目標對象</span><br />\n1. 不同年齡層<br />\n我相信現階段支持者大部份人是80/90後，必需爭取其他年齡層支持。<br />\n<br />\n2. 港豬型和理非<br />\n大家身邊和理非有無開始動搖，開始說前線太過火 ? 什至覺得和平集會遊行都要停一停 ? 又或者他們會覺得先讓步對政府釋出善意有用? 但事實一退就永不翻身，最終對不起付出性命的義士，被告暴動及受傷的義士！因此必需再次喚醒他們。<br />\n<br />\n3. 營造氣氛 鼓勵士氣<br />\n實體有連儂牆，但不是每區都有地方可貼，比如大型公屋村，政府地方嚴禁張貼。因此轉到網絡上，運動已持續逾兩個月，我相信政府既處理手法令到不少人感到灰心消極，希望大家能夠堅持初心，將力量凝聚在一起。<br />\n<br />\n4. 不問世事的人<br />\n只能說，希望多個途徑，能夠多個戰友。<br />\n<br />\n還有制衡 TVB選擇性報導 , 藍絲假新聞等等...<br />\n就算以上針對目標推測你都不認同，但實際換來成效會有好多意想不到的可能性。(只可以講: 唔做就一定無。 )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下介紹專題排板範例 :</span><br />\n7月21日元朗白衣人襲擊事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkebill.com/7%E6%9C%8821%E6%97%A5%E5%8...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkebill.com%2F7%25E6%259C%258821%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258...&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=8605fadd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkebill.com/7%E6%9C%8821%E6%97%A5%E5%8...</a><br />\n<br />\n由上而下<br />\n1. 清晰大標題<br />\n2. 簡單圖片文字時序<br />\n3. 影片連接<br />\n4. 事件爭議<br />\n5. 針對主題的訴求<br />\n<br />\nPS : 由於時間緊迫，人手有限，其他主題內容仍在努力完成中，必定在廣告推出前完成，如閣下對網站內容有任何意見，歡迎提出 <a href=\"https://www.hkebill.com/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkebill.com%2Fcontact%2F&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=37410aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkebill.com/contact/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">投放廣告位置</span><br />\n任何有使用Google 廣告的網站, 討論區 , 入門網站 , Youtube 等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQk2xuK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQk2xuK.jpg&h=5cf07d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下為廣告投放[每小時]預測數據</span><br />\n曝光次數 : 20萬 <br />\n點擊數 : 500 -1000<br />\n平均單次點擊出價 : $2.7 <br />\n費用 : $1350 - $2700<br />\n<br />\n*數據只作參考, 因我們會按需要不時調整目標對象、年齡層及廣告時段，而廣告設計吸引力亦影響點擊率成效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廣告投放預計日期</span><br />\n8月23日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標眾籌金額</span><br />\n$60萬 (保守估計平均每天2萬 x30日)<br />\n<br />\n我們不一定每天用2萬，視乎廣告效果及當時情況。如眾籌金額多於目標，亦都會全數投放在廣告費上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">使用廣告費證明</span><br />\n每天上載資料到網站，包括 Google ads 後台屏幕截圖及影片拍攝，後台操作清楚展示當天廣告洗費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網站安全問題</span><br />\n網站在外國，亦已用上 Cloudflare 提高網站安全性避免攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己香港自己救！請支持本地文宣！Like 及 share !</span>"},{"pid":"4afb318b2a1eded2caece3741ed3e4674a41f16d","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 ! Like &amp; share ! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d7e486c7128547ffc3420fc8881b7e3a8a41ed","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 ! Like &amp; share ! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7e6587f56318da5995dce8aaf182d5d4c1858b","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:15:35.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 ! Like &amp; share ! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c53408b8603e6fc31e4f1675579a69c8bee52e","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 ! Like &amp; share ! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef637835e54a3f36e6e73ad606bbc7f6896b2e96","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 ! Like &amp; share ! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730a80606e20af8159d1fdfe6bdc1133ab4453f0","tid":1486842,"uid":271234,"like":